Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:32.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}张开双臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:37.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:37.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:40.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:40.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告诉我在哪里
